accessibility.text: Rather than clutter up a landing page with discount offers and featured items, we wanted a clean and simple design so that users are not overwhelmed. Our research showed that in most cases, users are savvy in online bargain shopping, and often know what they are looking for when visiting a fan apparel site; making these featured items obsolete, and discount codes irritating to navigate through. We would still like to offer discounts to users, and felt the most logical place to put them is the Cart page, where this information is needed.
